{"tid":613736,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 莫少聰撇大肚洪欣　8年後先認數！","createTime":"2018-04-02T03:00:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-06T00:53:48.000Z","uid":48905,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"129919b8e3285fd97df49fa073b5562ffc9866ca","tid":613736,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T03:00:50.000Z","msg":"洪欣於2009年下嫁拍拖四年的內地男星張丹峰，雖然張丹峰比洪欣年輕10年，但對洪欣寵愛有加，並許下一生承諾：「我會用心照顧佢一輩子，愛佢一生一世。」而張丹峰更對洪欣為莫少聰所生的兒子張浩鋒視如己出，原名莫鎬廉的張浩鋒因洪欣改嫁改跟後父姓張為張鎬濂，後才改為張浩鋒，父子關係融洽。而洪欣亦在2014年為張丹峰誕下女兒張晞彤，一家四口樂融融。 <br />\n<br />\n洪欣最轟動的情史莫過於在1997年與莫少聰相戀，後於2000年獨自到加拿大秘密誕下兒子，惟未出世二人已分手收場，外間一直覺得生父是莫少聰，惟洪欣三緘其口，而莫少聰亦否認。直至2008年莫少聰才承認為生父，但洪欣則指過去的事情由它過去。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/02/105924_a4e0cd0ae4faa5c8261b2f5aca415d56.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F02%2F105924_a4e0cd0ae4faa5c8261b2f5aca415d56.png&h=f0a7e5d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"> 西...西女人洪欣當年同莫少聰甩拖後先誕子。</span>"},{"pid":"dbc5ba669a3b662875ba449d48efbcb227d0f9ba","tid":613736,"uid":29880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T03:04:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我</span></span>"},{"pid":"f5e463d124e080a3340076238aaf53ec1c740ce6","tid":613736,"uid":73346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dbc5ba669a3b662875ba449d48efbcb227d0f9ba","tid":613736,"uid":29880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T03:04:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T03:06:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">真</span></span>"},{"pid":"955335c0032105f52d9721697391674ca7241640","tid":613736,"uid":175976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T03:11:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span st